---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Guides - MB Therapeutics Blog">
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Guides</h1>
      <p>Guides complets sur les technologies et processus d'impression 3D pharmaceutique</p>
    </section>

    <section class="articles">
      <article class="article-card">
        <div class="article-meta">
          <span class="badge">Guide</span>
          <span class="reading-time">12 min de lecture</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Guide complet de l'impression 3D pharmaceutique</h2>
        <p>Découvrez les fondamentaux de l'impression 3D appliquée à la pharmacie hospitalière, les différentes technologies disponibles et leurs applications concrètes.</p>
        <a href="/guides/impression-3d-pharmaceutique" class="read-more">Lire le guide →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="article-card">
        <div class="article-meta">
          <span class="badge">Guide</span>
          <span class="reading-time">10 min de lecture</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Technologies d'impression 3D en pharmacie</h2>
        <p>Comparaison détaillée des différentes technologies disponibles pour l'impression de médicaments : FDM, SLA, SLS et leurs spécificités.</p>
        <a href="/guides/technologies-impression-3d" class="read-more">Lire le guide →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="article-card">
        <div class="article-meta">
          <span class="badge">Guide</span>
          <span class="reading-time">15 min de lecture</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Réglementation et impression 3D pharmaceutique</h2>
        <p>Comprendre le cadre réglementaire de l'impression 3D de médicaments en France et en Europe. Normes, bonnes pratiques et exigences qualité.</p>
        <a href="/guides/reglementation-impression-3d" class="read-more">Lire le guide →</a>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 0 4rem 0;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--primary-blue);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .articles {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .article-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .article-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--hover-shadow);
  }

  .article-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .badge {
    background: #E8F3FF;
    color: var(--primary-blue);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .reading-time {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .article-card h2 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .article-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .read-more {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--primary-blue);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .read-more:hover {
    color: var(--dark-blue);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .article-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .article-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
